body_html:
There seems to be a bug in SwapDimension1And2InTensor3WithNarrowMatrices from
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/kernels/conv_ops_gpu_3.cu.cc.
The method ignores the template parameter bool conjugate.
